            <h1 class="uppercase tracking-wider font-jersey text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-normal mb-1">
                Stories <span class="lowercase text-emerald-600/80">/ <span id="typewriter"
                                                                            class="after:content-['\_'] after:animate-blink italic font-normal"></span></span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-sm italic">Accounts that explain why things happen(ed) through context and perspective.</p>
        </header>
